01/06/2005
NICOSIA, Cyprus -- UN Undersecretary General for Political Affairs Kieran Prendergast met with Cyprus President Tassos Papadopoulos, according to a UN press release issued Tuesday (31 May). The UN envoy, who kicked off a several-day tour of the region, is expected to meet with Turkish Cypriot President Mehmet Ali Talat on Wednesday, before travelling on to Ankara and Athens. (UN Web site, NTV - 31/05/05)
